    "59 developed a feature-based approach for Brunnstrom Stage and Mobility Index classification.",
    "Acceleration signals containing movement information of patients while doing rehabilitation exercises were collected using an IMUbased body sensor network.",
    "The signals were segmented into individual exercise repetitions through peak detection.",
    "Dimensionality reduction was applied to the signals using principal component analysis and input to an adaptive neuro-fuzzy inference system for Brunnstrom stage classification.",
    "Ghorbel et al."
